incident_updates.body:
Following a thorough investigation, our team has determined that a number of servers in this rack (46B21) have been impacted. All impacted servers in rack 46B21 have been restored, and our teams are diligently working to restore the remaining ones in racks 46B19 and 46B18.

We will keep you updated on the progress and resolution.
We apologize for any inconvenience caused and appreciate your understanding.

We have determined the origin of the incident affecting our Dedicated Servers offer on the specific rack. Here are some supplementary details : Start time : 04/02/2025 14:10 UTC Customers Impact : Some servers in racks 46B19 and 46B18 are temporarily unavailable. Root Cause : This incident is caused by a cooling system issue. Ongoing Actions : The incident has been identified and our teams are mobilised to restore service as quickly as possible. We will keep you updated on the progress and resolution. We apologize for any inconvenience caused and appreciate your understanding.

We are currently experiencing an incident affecting our Dedicated Servers offering, which is causing temporary availability issues in the racks 46B19, 46B18 in RBX6. Here is detail for this incident : Start time : 04/02/2025 14:10 UTC Customers Impact : Some servers in racks 46B19, 46B18 are temporarily unavailable. Ongoing Actions : Our teams are investigating to determine the origin of the incident to fix it. We will keep you updated on the progress and resolution. We apologize for any inconvenience caused and appreciate your understanding.

We are currently experiencing an event affecting our Bare Metal Cloud offer. Start time : 04/02/2025 14:10 UTC Our teams are fully committed to investigating this issue and working towards a resolution as soon as possible. As investigations are ongoing, we will share any new findings or updates with you as soon as possible. We apologize for any inconvenience caused and appreciate your understanding.

incident_updates.body: As part of our continuous improvement plan, maintenance is scheduled on our Baremetal offer. Start time : 05/02/2025 11:00 UTC End time : 05/02/2025 11:30 UTC Service impact : Starting next month, the EfiBootloaderPath will be required as an input for BringYourOwnImage and BringYourOwnLinux operating systems. Service improvement : This change will enable customers to customize their EFI bootloader path, if you have any questions or need further clarification, please contact Support. Follow the links below for the documentation. BringYourOwnLinux: https://ovh.to/8stqmx3 BringYourOwnImage: https://ovh.to/fRZWyVr Thank you for your understanding.
